highlights.text: “All I Want for Christmas Is You” by Mariah Carey is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 142 spots at #40.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Is It Over Now? (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)” is the highest at #1.
“Standing Next to You” by Jung Kook is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #19.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 181 weeks straight.
